      "description": "Available is a museum-grade E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six and a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. This specimen is mechanically flawless, with the double VANOS system fully overhauled and rod bearings proactively replaced with updated VAC coated shells. The rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to ensure chassis rigidity under high lateral loads. The suspension retains its factory geometry with fresh bushings, and the limited-slip differential operates silently with crisp engagement. Finished in Alpine White with original paint depth readings, the exterior is paired with pristine Imola Red Nappa leather. Every toggle and switch retains its tactile feedback, reflecting a vehicle that has been maintained with obsessive technical precision. This is a turnkey, investment-quality icon for the driver who demands mechanical perfection.",
